lead_paragraph: Defending champion Tomas Berdych defeated Czech countryman Jiri Vesely 7-6 (1), 3-6, 6-2 in the Shenzhen Open quarterfinals on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Berdych Beats Vesely to Make Shenzhen Semis With Gasquet
